data.description: Sitting on over 1.6 acres, this corner lot beauty is ready for it's new owner. Plenty of room for outdoor activities, the back of the lot features plenty of shade. Inside you will find surprising updates, such as granite counter tops, new floors as well as updated bathrooms. The huge master suite offers plenty of room to get away from everyday stress. Home features covered front porch and a large covered deck in the rear. A nice white vinyl fence surrounds 3 sides of the lot. Seller has survey. Foundation repairs completed in 2021, further information can be found in documents. Information deemed reliable but not guaranteed. Buyer or Buyer's agent should verify all information.
